node.text: I’m a little scared to post this for many reasons. This is my own very short, very not great VERSION of Nuvole Bianche.  I’m not a pianist and as much as I wish I could move my fingers like a majestic gazelle I cannot...(yet)  I don’t read music, I don’t have training. I teach myself and I love to play. So yes I know this isn’t how you play this song in the slightest. But sitting at the piano getting incredibly frustrated with myself for days in a row and having this be the outcome..makes me a little proud and happy.

node.title: An extremely amateur take on the great Ludovico Einaudi

node.text: Dance into the weekend with us AND WATCH THE KISSING BOOTH 2 ON NETFLIX!!! This is the full version that we shot of the final arcade scene with Marco and Elle. We danced the entire day which was killer on my shin splints but my dance partner made it all worth it. This was a really exhausting day but more fun than anything else. I miss this a lot 🥺❤️

node.text:
It’s hard to put into words how loved I feel today. So hard that the best I could do to try was cry from the overwhelming feeling of joy multiple times. I want to thank everyone who’s wished me a happy birthday today for your lovely words/videos/edits and more. Here’s a small glimpse into the most gorgeous video my love made for me which also made me cry…a lot. 

It’s been an amazing birthday and even though I miss them, I can feel all my family’s love from miles and miles away. Hello there 22, you’re off to a wonderful start. Thank you for making my day so beautiful @stevenpiet
